# Risk Assessment: HR System Migration


## Top Risks & Mitigations
| Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| Data mapping gaps | High | Medium | Conduct field-by-field reviews; use reconciliation reports. |
| Parallel payroll mismatch | High | Medium | Two payroll parallels; variance threshold ≤0.5%; corrective playbook. |
| Access/role issues at go‑live | Medium | Medium | Pre-provision roles; UAT sign-off on role matrix. |
| Integration breaks | High | Low | Contract tests for inbound/outbound; smoke tests post-cutover. |
| User adoption | Medium | Medium | Targeted training; floor support; job aids. |
| Timeline slippage | Medium | Medium | Critical path tracking; weekly steering updates; scope gatekeeping. |
